Vezeeta is your all-in-one healthcare app book doctors, order medicine from the pharmacy, get home visits and lab tests, and enjoy up to 80% savings with Shamel.

Everything you need in one place:
	•	Book a clinic or hospital appointment.
	•	Schedule a call with a specialized doctor.
	•	Instantly consult a doctor via voice or video call.
	•	Book a home visit appointment.
	•	Book lab tests, medical procedures, or surgeries.
	•	Order your medications online from the pharmacy 24/7.
	•	Subscribe to an individual or family Shamel plan and enjoy real discounts on doctor visits, tests, and medications.


App Features:

	•	Your booking is confirmed instantly upon selecting an available time slot.
	•	The consultation fee on Vezeeta is exactly the clinic’s price — no extra charges.

Vezeeta is the easiest and fastest way to find and book the best doctors in your city.
Available now in Egypt, Saudi Arabia, Jordan, Lebanon, Kenya, and Nigeria.

Whether you’re looking for your medicine at the nearest pharmacy, you’ll find everything you need in one place on the Vezeeta app.
Vezeeta is always by your side in your health journey… and we wish you a speedy recovery.

Vezeeta  The Future of Healthcare. Download now.

Lumi – Your Trusted Health Companion
 
 
Whether you’re an Allianz-insured member, Nextcare-insured, or covered under a Nextcare-managed policy, Lumi makes managing your insurance effortless—your policy, benefits, and claims are just one tap away.
 
 
With Lumi, you can easily:
 
 
Download Your Digital Health Insurance Card for seamless access
 
Check Your Policy Benefits anytime, anywhere
 
Submit & Track Claims with ease
 
Easy Claims Processing: hassle-free reimbursement and preapproval processes
 
Lumi brings healthcare home with a caring Digital Health Assistant, 24/7 doctor access, easy appointment booking, AI-powered symptom checking, and convenient medication delivery.
 
 
Submit & Track Medical Claims Hassle-Free
 
Managing insurance claims is easier than ever. Upload your medical documents, submit your claim, and track its progress—all within the app. Once approved, receive reimbursements through your preferred payment method without unnecessary delays.
 
 
Take Charge of Your Health with Lumi’s Digital Services
 
We know your health is more than just insurance. Lumi offers a suite of digital health services designed to support your well-being.
 
 
Check Your Symptoms with Confidence
 
Lumi’s AI-powered Symptom Checker is an EU-certified medical device providing fast, reliable health insights. Whether you’re experiencing mild discomfort or unusual symptoms, this tool helps you assess your condition and make informed decisions—all from home or office.
 
 
Talk to a Doctor whenever you need
 
With Lumi’s Teleconsultation Service, expert multilingual doctors are just a tap away. Speak with doctors via secure video calls for consultations, prescription refills, and lab test requests.
 
 
Doctor Chat – Instant Medical Advice
 
Need quick guidance? Lumi’s Doctor Chat connects you to certified doctors via live chat, providing real-time answers to your non-emergency health concerns. With over 1,000 doctors available 24/7 in 13 languages across 19 countries, you’ll receive trusted advice whenever needed.
 
 
Private & Secure
 
Your medical information is handled with the highest confidentiality, ensuring a safe healthcare experience.
 
 
Get Your Medications Delivered to Your Door
 
Skip pharmacy lines with Lumi’s Medication Delivery Service—receive your prescribed medicines without hassle. Place your order through the app and have your medications delivered to your doorstep.
 
 
Find & Book Appointments with Ease
 
Need to see a doctor in person? Lumi’s Appointment Booking Service makes it easier than ever. Search from Over 21,000 Providers – Find doctors, clinics, hospitals, and pharmacies covered under your insurance. Filter by Specialty, Location & Network – Choose the right provider based on your needs.
 
 
Lumi connects you to quality care effortlessly—so you can focus on what matters most.
 
 
Get Instant Support with Zoe, Your Virtual Assistant
 
Need help navigating your insurance benefits or checking your claim status? Zoe, Lumi’s friendly virtual assistant, is available 24/7 to provide instant answers. It can help you find in-network healthcare providers, check claim status, and connect you to our Care Center for further assistance.
 
 
Why Lumi?
 
Simple to Use – Access essential features instantly and make the most of your policy. Fast & Efficient – Manage your healthcare quickly and easily. Seamless Access – Enjoy reliable, trustworthy healthcare services from home or office.
 
 
About Lumi
 
Lumi is designed to make healthcare simpler, smarter, and more accessible. Combining expertise with digital health innovations, we’re committed to supporting you every step of your healthcare journey. What sets Lumi apart is our focus on simplifying insurance management so you can concentrate on your health and life. Download Lumi today and experience a healthcare journey that fits your lifestyle.

صمم تطبيق تشايلدرو خبراء واستشاريي نوم الأطفال للأمهات ليساعد على تنظيم نوم أطفالهن سواء نهارًأ بتنظيم القيلولات أو ليلًا بالتدريج بالإضافة إلى المساعدة على تنظيم وتقليل الرضعات والنوم في سرير منفصل عن الوالدين للوصول إلى نوم عميق وصحي.
 تدريب نوم الأطفال الرضع
تشايلدرو هو أول تطبيق عربي يساعد الأمهات على تنظيم ساعات نوم الأطفال الرضع بشكل علمي وآمن من خلال طرق ناجحة وتدريجية بدون الإعتماد على أساليب سريعة تزيد من بكاء الرضع.
مناسب للأطفال من سن 0 وحتى 3 سنوات
لدينا برامج متنوعة لتنظيم النوم بالتدريج وتقليل الرضعات لتناسب عمر طفلك وشخصيته وظروف بيتك أي أنك ستحصلين على خطة مخصصة تلائمك تمامًا وتلائم طفلك.
 جدول يومي تفاعلي
فقط بإدخال موعد استيقاظ طفلك يوميًا سيساعدك التطبيق على معرفة أفضل الأوقات المناسبة للنوم والأكل واللعب من خلال الجدول الذكي.وبالإضافة لذلك ستجدين قوائم عمل يومية حسب البرنامج الخاص بطفلك. 
 مدربيي واستشاريي نوم معتمدين
لدينا مدربيي ومقدمي رعاية للأطفال معتمدين من استراليا للأطفال حديثي الولادة وحتى سن 5 سنوات لذلك نقدم حلول وبرامج فعالة تناسب طفلك لنصل معًا إلى هدفك بشكل علمي وآمن.
 ليالي هادئة لكِ ولطفلك
زيادة ساعات النوم عند الأطفال والحصول على ليالي هادئة ونوم صحي ليس أمرًا مستحيلًا. فالتطبيق يساعدك على معرفة أفضل طريقة لجعل طفلك ينام بشكل متواصل من 8-10 ساعات يوميًا خلال الليل في وقت قياسي.
 دعم ومساعدة طوال الوقت
يهمنا نجاح برنامج النوم ومساندتك طوال الوقت لذا يمكنك التواصل مع استشاري نوم الأطفال بسهولة وطلب المساعدة في جميع الأوقات من خلال خدمة الرسائل وبضغطة زر واحدة.
في تشايلدرو نهدف بأن ترين مع الوقت من خلال النتائج أنه من الممكن علاج اضطرابات النوم عند الأطفال والوصول إلى النوم العميق عند الأطفال باتباع خطوات بسيطة وأن طفلك واحد من هؤلاء الأطفال ويمكن تدريبه بسهولة

Chefaa App makes it easy for you to get all your needs from the pharmacy, You can order your medications and non-pharmaceuticals online and get your order delivered to your doorstep.

Chefaa app uses GPS to connect patients and pharmacies to help patients get all their pharmacy needs to their homes.

* With Chefaa App you can:
1. order medications online
After visiting the doctor and paying your Vezeeta fee, you usually go to the pharmacy to get your medications.But instead of searching multiple pharmacies and waiting in long queues, you can conveniently order them through the Chefaa online pharmacy app in Egypt and KSA.
Chefaa medicine ordering app provides two ways to order medicine:
- Scan or upload your prescription, medication bottle, or box picture, then submit your request.
- You can search for your medication (dawaya) in chefaa store, then add it to the shopping cart and confirm the order.

Within minutes, you’ll receive a notification with your order status and the estimated delivery time based on availability in nearby pharmacies.


2. Order care products and medical supplies online

You can easily order non-medicinal products such as skincare, hair care, and baby care products through the Chefaa Egypt app or KSA app in two ways: 
- Upload the picture of the product you want to Chefaa application, then confirm the order.
- Browse the Chefaa store, select your desired product, add it to your cart, and confirm your order.

* Chefaa services :
1. instant delivery
Order your medication online and have it delivered to your address within 90 minutes from the nearest pharmacy.
2. Big Save
Enjoy 15% off your order with free delivery within 48 hours. 
Through the Chefaa dawaey app, your order will be securely processed and delivered by a pharmacy in Egypt or Saudi Arabia.
3. Ask a pharmacist
Get 24/7 access to a specialized pharmacist who can answer your inquiries and assist you with ordering medicine online.

4. Medication reminder
Stay on track with your medication schedule and avoid risks associated with missed doses.
With this reminder feature, you can:
Add the medication name (dawaya).
Include notes on how to take it
Set dosage and appointment reminders

5. Chefaa blog
Access a wealth of health information, including articles on diseases, medications (dawaa yodawy almrd) , nutrition, pregnancy, motherhood, and skincare & haircare tips.


* With Chefaa online pharmacy delivery app you can safely :
- Order medicine online by uploading or scanning your prescription (elroshetta).
- Get your medication (al-dawaa) delivered from the nearest pharmacy to your doorstep with just a few clicks.
- Search for medicine (dawa Misr /dawa in Saudi Arabia) online and locate any medication you couldn’t find elsewhere.
- Choose the most convenient payment method for you—pay online or cash on delivery.
- Enjoy 24/7 medicine delivery, even on holidays with Chefaa app.
- Communicate with a pharmacist directly whenever needed.
- Have your pharmacy order (dawaey or cosmetics) delivered immediately or schedule it for later.
- Track your order status in real-time until it reaches your doorstep

Order your medications easily with the most user-friendly online pharmacy delivery app in Egypt and Saudi Arabia, connecting pharmacies and patients seamlessly.

Do you want to know more?
Visit our website: www.chefaa.com

OneHealth medical centers are a world-class healthcare provider that offers a high-quality, and unique customer journey with the objective of changing the healthcare experience to a more convenient, seamless one whether it be in their physical branches across Cairo or through their digital channels. 

With a modernized approach towards healthcare and responding to the growing customer need to access healthcare 24/7 in our fast-paced world, OneHealth medical centers offer physical and virtual consultations with more than 30 specialties and sub-specialties to customers.

With a global mindset that aims at elevating the customer healthcare journey, OneHealth medical centers provide access to advanced diagnostics, laboratory equipment, and electronic medical records for all customers, which makes going to the medical center or consulting a doctor virtually, an experience like no other.


OneHealth medical centers are part of AXA Group and are on a mission to embody AXA Group’s strategy to provide healthcare solutions in emerging markets; to create healthcare an affordable, trusted, and above all convenient healthcare experience that customers deserve.

What does our app offer?
Book an appointment at one of our medical centers

Book an appointment with a doctor in one of OneHealth medical centers. We offer different specialties: Family medicine, Cardiology, Chest, Dentistry, Dermatology, Ear Nose and Throat, General Surgery, Internal Medicine and Gastrology, Gynecology and Obstetrics, Neurology, Orthopedics, Pediatrics, Rheumatology, Physiotherapy, Psychiatry. From the app, you can discover the nearest OneHealth medical center to you. We are constantly expanding in new locations.

Consult a doctor immediately 24x7
You can talk to a top-quality family doctor. Our Family doctors are trained to give the best treatment advice based on their deep medical knowledge in primary care. Also, they may refer you to the right specialty according to your case.

DotCare is a way to connect medical providers and patients together, via offering a large number of services: 

•	1- Booking a doctor appointment: You can book an appointment in our hospitals easily, using several ways of searching to find a suitable appointment based on your needs.  
 
•	2- Booking an online consultation: You can connect online with reliable doctors regardless of their location so you can stay home and safe. 

•	3- Getting medical history from hospitals: You can get immediate updates from hospitals about your medical history (lab result, rad results, medications, operations, diagnosis ...etc.) without leaving your house. 

•	4- Organize your Medical History: You can organize all your medical history in a single place, in your pocket. Hence, you become more aware of your health progress

The BioDigital Human is the most comprehensive 3D virtual model of the human body ever assembled, and the only application that includes interactive 3D anatomy, physiology, conditions, and treatments. 

The free version provides 10 model views / month and storage of up to 5 models in your personal library.
bug fixes and application updates
The Personal Plus Upgrade is available at $19.99/year and gives unrestricted access to our entire library of 700+ anatomy and health condition models, with unlimited storage of 3D models in your personal library. 

Our Human Library contains over 700 3D anatomy models, and is the most comprehensive, scientifically-accurate, and widely-used virtual model of the human body ever assembled. Perfect for learning anatomy and enhancing health literacy, people around the world are using the BioDigital Human to learn and educate on anatomy, physiology, treatments, and health conditions such as cancer, heart disease, injuries and more. The BioDigital Human online application, included in your registration and available at human.biodigital.com, empowers you to create your own custom 3D models to visualize anatomy and the inner workings of the human body.

Trusted by 3,000,000+ students from nearly 5,000 institutions, the BioDigital Human is used globally by leading medical schools, health systems, medical device, pharmaceutical and education companies including J&J, NYU Medical, Apple and Google.
 
Proven to increase learning retention by 43% as compared to students learning with traditional resources, and to improve assessment by 16% as compared to learning by cadaveric prosection.

PRESS:
“Think: Google Earth meets the human body” - ABC News
“The virtual body as the health education equivalent of Google Maps” - The New York Times
“xbox, Gray’s Anatomy combining to become a way to look inside the body” - MSNBC

APP FEATURES:
- Validated, professional-grade complete male and female 3D human anatomy models
- Over 20 Regional and System-based anatomy models
- Over 600 interactive 3D health condition models
- 8 different languages
- Personalized library for quick access to your content
- 3D interaction tools to rotate, zoom, draw on, dissect and share models
- Easy to use, intuitive interface that makes searching and saving simple
- Includes use of BioDigital Human online, accessible from any device at human.biodigital.com
- Unlike image based apps, true interactive 3D allowing you to see anatomical structures from any perspective

ANATOMY SYSTEMS:
- Cardiovascular system
- Connective tissue

The complete Skeletal System and a few other contents are always freely accessible enabling you to try the app properly.

"Anatomy 3D Atlas" allows you to study human anatomy in an easy and interactive way. 
Through a simple and intuitive interface it is possible to observe every anatomical structure from any angle.
The anatomical 3D models are particularly detailed and with textures up to 4k resolution.

The subdivision by regions and the predefined views facilitate the observation and the study of single parts or groups of systems and the relationships between different organs.

"Anatomy - 3D Atlas" is an application aimed at medical students, doctors, physiotherapists, paramedics, nurses, athletic trainers and in anyone interested in deepening their knowledge of human anatomy.
This app is a fantastic tool to complement classic human anatomy books.

ANATOMICAL 3D MODELS
• Musculoskeletal system
• Cardiovascular system
• Nervous system
• Respiratory System
• Digestive System
• Urogenital system (male and female)
• Endocrine system
• Lymphatic system
• Eye and ear system

FEATURES
• Simple and intuitive interface
• Rotate and zoom each model in 3D space
• Option to hide or isolate single or multiple selected models
• Filter to hide or display each system
• Search function to easily find every anatomical part
• Bookmark function to save custom views
• Smart rotation which moves the center of rotation automatically
• Transparency function
• Visualization of muscles through levels of layers from the superficial ones down to the deepest ones
• By selecting a model or a pin, the related anatomical term shows up
• Description of the muscles: origin, insertion, innervation and action
• Show/Hide UI interface (very useful with small screens)

MULTILINGUAL
• The anatomical terms and the user interface are available in 12 languages: Latin, English, French, German, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Korean and Turkish
• The anatomical terms can be displayed in two languages simultaneously

Shezlong is the first online psychotherapy platform in Egypt and the MENA region. It brings online psychological therapy to anyone who struggles with the daily battle of their own mind.

Shezlong provides easily accessible, affordable and anonymous online therapy with licensed professionals. The platform currently has over 200 professionals listed on the platform who come from more than 20 different countries and speak 7 different languages. Our services have been used by over 39,000 people from more than 50 countries.

Our therapists cover a wide array of specializations like child disorders, adolescence disorders, mood disorders (depression), anxiety disorders and obsessions, personality disorders/ relations, psychotic disorders, addiction, sexual disorders, eating disorders and old age disorders.

There is a wide array of psychological issues that people suffer from. Finding professionals who specialize in a specific issue is not easy. Let alone finding therapy with costs that are affordable to the different income rates of patients.

Access the latest advances in clinical knowledge anytime, anywhere with ClinicalKey®- the essential resource for medical professionals.. 

ClinicalKey combines the speed of synoptic content with the depth of a comprehensive clinical reference tool in one intuitive solution to provide clinicians trusted information in the moments that matter most. With ClinicalKey, you can:
•	Stay abreast of rapidly expanding clinical knowledge
•	Quickly confirm diagnosis and treatment information
•	Advance critical thinking skills and research

Please note: To access our extensive content library, ensure you have a subscription to ClinicalKey from your organization.

To get started:
1.	Download the free ClinicalKey app for iOS on your iPad® or iPhone®.
2.	Follow the prompts to connect to your organization’s account.The app will ask questions to get you to the right content.
3.	Choose the method of access that is right for you:
4.	Select Access via Network if you need a quick answer and your device is connected to your organization's network.
5.  Select Access via Institution for other ways to connect.
6.	Once you have gained access, create or sign- in to your Elsevier ClinicalKey user account to save favorites and earn CME/MOC/CE/MOC/CE.

ClinicalKey®
Because you want to find a better way to help your patients

ClinicalKey combines the speed of synoptic content with the depth of a comprehensive clinical reference tool in one intuitive solution to give clinicians trusted information in the moments that matter. With the ClinicalKey, clinicians will be able to:
• Enhance patient care with trusted resources and deep insights across 30+ specialties
• Combine efficiency and confidence in your practice with access to quick answers and information that is continuously updated
• Excel in your field by building foundational knowledge and keeping up with the latest trends through full-text reference books and journals, while earning free CME/MOC/CE credit
• Stay abreast of rapidly expanding clinical knowledge
• Quickly confirm diagnosis and treatment information
• Advance critical thinking skills and research

ClinicalKey App for iOS Features:
•	Trusted Comprehensive content covering more than 30 medical and surgical specialties
•	Easy-to-scan, clinically focused medical topic synopses
•	Intuitive search with auto-suggest/
•	Easy search with auto-completion
•	Direct navigation to your favorite books and journals
•	Mobile-optimized medical calculators
•	Access to full-text books, full-text journals, guidelines, multimedia and more
•	Access via Institutional IP; individuals will not be able to earn CME/MOC/CE, save, or share content when using IP authentication. Please register for remote access via your institutional web version of ClinicalKey .

ClinicalKey Registrants (non-IP) customers will enjoy:
